column4: Help. I put in a cdrom into my CD Drive (cdrom0) and now it wont eject. Nothing will open it. Gives me an error. I'm about ready to force eject it, is that safe?
Help. I put in a cdrom into my CD Drive (cdrom0) and now it wont eject. Nothing will open it. Gives me an error. I'm about ready to force eject it, is that safe?
have you tried typing "eject" in a terminal window
Yes. It says it can not eject it
